    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered every single weekend. It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and drives like an absolute dream, this is the one. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
