    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen is mechanically pristine, boasting a comprehensive service history that includes a professional VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains factory-perfect with no bushing degradation, providing the sharp turn-in response these chassis are known for. The exterior retains its original deep luster with no paint imperfections, while the interior leather maintains its factory matte finish with zero bolster wear. A concours-level example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and high-speed stability.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
