      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been maintained to a showroom standard, kept in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather interior remains supple and fragrant, showing no signs of wear or creasing. Every electronic component and feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless; the engine bay is spotless, and all service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with full documentation available. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
