    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in absolutely pristine shape\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it! \u2728",
