      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade specimen of the E46 chassis, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This unit exhibits flawless VANOS timing and has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement to ensure mechanical longevity. The naturally aspirated induction system delivers instantaneous throttle response through six individual throttle bodies, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The subframe has been meticulously inspected and reinforced, maintaining structural rigidity. Finished in its original factory coating with zero paint depth variance, the exterior remains showroom-fresh, while the interior retains its factory leather scent and tactile integrity. A true driver\u2019s car for the discerning collector who demands peak mechanical performance and aesthetic perfection.",
